After creatin a scene:
change the renderer to Cycles and oneof preview to render view by pressing Z and select Rendered. 

1- Optimization: Removing hidden faces
2- position check for Z fighting 
3- Fixing faces orientation
4- Normalize scales: in object mode select all objects with A, press Ctrl+A to open the Aooly menu and choose Scale. You can't see a difference, but all of the object scales have been applied to their geometries instead. This way, all our objects now have a scale of 1.
5- create or open UV Editor area, select object and go to Edit Mode to see the uv unwraped of object 
